name: Zet Universe Development Platform
body:
### Welcome!
Zet Universe offers developers to use custom data sources and data processors within the platform.

### Authors and Contributors
In 2015, Daniel Kornev (@danielkornev) and Danila Korablin (@dkorablin) started working together on the extendable platform for Zet Universe. Danila Korablin's SAL (Software Abstraction Layer) is used as the plugin infrastructure foundation. 

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with Zet Universe Development Platform? Check out our [contact support](http://www.zetuniverse.com/contact-us.html) and weâ€™ll help you sort it out.
